com.github.cjwizard

Class FlatWizardSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      • java.util.HashMap<String,Object>
        • com.github.cjwizard.FlatWizardSettings
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WizardSettings, Serializable, Cloneable, Map<String,Object>

    public class FlatWizardSettings
extends HashMap<String,Object>
implements WizardSettings
    This settings can save pairs of key and values in a plain HashMap. Note that this class doesn't implement the transaction model, and so newPage(String), rollBack() and commit() methods don't do anything.
    Author:
    ddearing
